author: daggny_taggart
content: WEBSITE      |      INSTAGRAM      |      TWITTER      |     To participate Instagram bounty - please join our Instagram and post proof of join and submit the form here https://forms.gle/SaYyNuJMbfPDyFWaAIt has to be an active instagram account, at least 1 year old and have not less than 20 publications.  Accounts with empty profile images, fake followers will be banned during payout evenif we won?t spot it during time preceding payout day.Payouts will be made according to the amount of followers you have:500 followers - 1500 followers  5 stakes1501 followers - 4500 followers - 10 stakes4500 - 30000 - 12 stakes30000 + 20 stakesAnd based on a biweekly activity - liking, commenting, sharingIf you have more than 50 k of active engaged followers - please contact us for a special payout plan. To participate you will need to follow our account,  regularly like, comment and postat least one story per week featuring our Instagram account.  To participate in TWITTER BOUNTY  - please join our  Twitter and post proof of join and submit the form here https://forms.gle/YPc3b2hTox4YWr579It has to be an active Twitter account, at least 1 year old and have not less than 20 publications.  Accounts with empty profile images, fake followers will be banned during payout evenif we won?t spot it during time preceding payout day. Payouts will be made according to the amount of followers you have:500 followers - 1500 followers  5 stakes1501 followers - 4500 followers - 10 stakes4500 - 30000 - 12 stakes30000 + 15 stakesAnd based on a biweekly activity - liking, commenting sharingIf you have more than 50 k of active engaged followers - please contact us for a special payout plan. To participate you will need to follow our account,  regularly like, comment and share at least one post per week featuring our Twitter account.
